Island name data

Source: R/data.R
island_areas.Rd

A collection of island names, their areas, and their elevations found using ArcGIS

Usage

island_areas

Format

'island_areas'

A data frame with 26376 rows and 5 variables:

OBJECTID_1

integer Object ID from ArcGIS

COUNT

integer Number of cells within island, from ArcGIS

AREA

double Area of the island

MAX

integer Maximum elevation of the island

Name

character Name of the island
